NARRATOR: Ford debuted the
small, economic Falcon in 1959

00:00:36.286 --> 00:00:39.873
for the 1960 model year as a
response to a growing recession

00:00:39.873 --> 00:00:42.000
and the immense popularity
of cheap imports

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.544
like the Volkswagen Beetle,
and it immediately began

00:00:44.544 --> 00:00:46.337
outselling the competition.

00:00:46.337 --> 00:00:49.716
Ford beat them to the punch
when it came to naming, as well.

00:00:49.716 --> 00:00:52.010
