both Ford and Chrysler

00:00:52.010 --> 00:00:54.721
were developing small
cars to be named Falcons,

00:00:54.721 --> 00:00:57.182
but Ford registered the
name with the Automobile

00:00:57.182 --> 00:01:00.935
Manufacturers Association just
20 minutes ahead of Chrysler,

00:01:00.935 --> 00:01:02.395
winning the naming rights.

00:01:02.395 --> 00:01:04.314
The Falcon platform
would eventually

00:01:04.314 --> 00:01:08.026
